com.ibm.team.repository.common

Interface IHelperType.IRegistry

  • Enclosing interface:
    IHelperType

    public static interface IHelperType.IRegistry
    Static registry used to locate helper types.

    Example usage: 

                    public interface ISomeClass extends ISomeClassHandle {
                public static final IHelperType HELPER_TYPE = IHelperType.IRegistry.INSTANCE
                      .getHelperType(SomePackage.eINSTANCE.getSomeClass().getName(),
                              SomePackage.eNS_URI);

    • Method Detail

      • getHelperType

        IHelperType getHelperType(java.lang.String name,
                        java.lang.String modelUri)
        Locates a helper type given its name and its model URI.
        Parameters:
        name - The helper type's name; must not be null
        modelUri - the helper type's model URI; must not be null
        Returns:
        the located helper type or null if the helper type name and model URI pair was not located in the helper type registry

      • getAllHelperTypes

        IHelperType[] getAllHelperTypes()
        Locates all helper types. Abstract types will be excluded.
        Returns:
        all helper types; never null

      • getAllHelperTypes

        IHelperType[] getAllHelperTypes(boolean includeAbstractTypes)
        Locates all helper types.
        Parameters:
        includeAbstractTypes - indicates whether abstract types should be included in the returned collection
        Returns:
        all helper types; never null
